Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.84,0:00:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.07,0:02:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"Money x Bonds" {\an}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.70,0:02:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning! Genzo, this morning let's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.08,0:02:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good boy... You're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.38,0:02:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Carmilla came home in\Nthe morning again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.22,0:02:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.88,0:02:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody's the same as usual today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.76,0:02:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, I'm making breakfast!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.93,0:02:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Genzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.85,0:02:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you're back, Katherine?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.02,0:02:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Altena!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.36,0:02:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the princess of a kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.86,0:02:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very noble!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.94,0:02:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you keep forgetting?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.36,0:02:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.74,0:02:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.66,0:02:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, for now, I'm not\Ngoing to worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.54,0:02:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Genzo, today I need you to promise\Nyou'll do your duty as a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.54,0:02:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.30,0:02:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never learn, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:03:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're like an obsessive stalker.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.01,0:03:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling a stalker?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.18,0:03:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Shigure, can you get me the salt?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.97,0:03:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The breakfast in this household\Nis always so bland...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.93,0:03:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.65,0:03:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we've all finished our meal,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.36,0:03:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Genzo...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.86,0:03:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.19,0:03:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to my knights,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.07,0:03:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Demon King from another world\Nattacked a village of orcs nearby...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.33,0:03:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. The orcs said the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.33,0:03:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this Demon King like, you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.67,0:03:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You knew, and yet\Nyou still did nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name was MAO, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.76,0:03:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.80,0:03:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Genzo! Genzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.89,0:03:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the Demon King\Nfrom another world like?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.10,0:03:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he was MAO,\Nthat's all I can say...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an obvious lie, Mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.19,0:04:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Genzo is a monster without\Na trace of compassion in him...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.32,0:04:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of life did you live where\Nyou got to know the Demon King, Genzo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.28,0:04:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.16,0:04:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why he did it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.66,0:04:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but this Demon King from another\Nworld mercilessly struck down
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.25,0:04:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the orcs on his own side.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.33,0:04:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no telling what other\Nhorrible things he may do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.59,0:04:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.09,0:04:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's how you can tell\Nhe's from another world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.09,0:04:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't care about friendship\Nbetween us monsters at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.76,0:04:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Us monsters"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.68,0:04:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible that the people of\Nthis town may be his next target.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.82,0:04:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.66,0:04:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Altena...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.20,0:04:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to take Hiroyuki for\Na walk. So please move.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.46,0:05:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can shake like a newborn deer,\Nbut I still won't love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.63,0:05:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.93,0:05:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroyuki's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.52,0:05:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.94,0:05:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the way the orcs\Nreacted, he must be close.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.82,0:05:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.36,0:05:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, show me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.86,0:05:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? What are you doing?\NCut it out, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.07,0:05:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Joanna! Get this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.29,0:05:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He nabbed something from the orc village.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.96,0:05:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?\NI mean it! Are you that dumb?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.08,0:05:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it's something naughty!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.13,0:05:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Shut up! Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.17,0:05:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naughty? I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.30,0:05:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But let me see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.88,0:05:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.93,0:05:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you showing my lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.06,0:06:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This angle. This bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.06,0:06:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.73,0:06:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've finally found you,\NAnimal Mask! Genzo Shibata!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.28,0:06:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Joanna, this is Carmilla, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.28,0:06:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She probably fell under\Nthe hero's sway, just like the orcs!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.58,0:06:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's just a lesser vampire.\NAnd her mistress is worthless anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.46,0:06:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Lindabulea also...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.67,0:06:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's doubtless the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.13,0:06:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll avenge your defeat.\NIt's the least I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.73,0:06:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aww, they took it from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.81,0:06:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It had all that stuff about "death grip"\Nand "unbearable shame."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.44,0:06:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was probably really naughty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroyuki! Hiroyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.57,0:06:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.83,0:06:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Genzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.66,0:06:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen Hiroyuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.16,0:07:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.21,0:07:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.67,0:07:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.17,0:07:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hiroyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.76,0:07:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally Genzo would notice\Nthat I changed my shampoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.01,0:07:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I thinking? How silly of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.27,0:07:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.27,0:07:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.32,0:07:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That animal doesn't matter, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.78,0:07:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Carmilla, Genzo does a lot for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.66,0:07:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a responsibility\Nto help him look for Hiroyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.29,0:07:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he's very important\Nto me... as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.59,0:07:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.92,0:07:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Princess Buttocks...\NI mean, Princess Altena!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.39,0:07:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen anybody named\NHiroyuki around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.64,0:08:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually it's an animal,\Na brown beast about this size...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.73,0:08:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.90,0:08:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.61,0:08:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! It's Princess Buttocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.98,0:08:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Buttocks! Princess Buttocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.95,0:08:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The scent drops off around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.29,0:08:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was he taken away in a bag\Nor some kind of box?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.09,0:08:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which would mean\Nthe crime was planned...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.42,0:08:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is something wrong, Shigure?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.38,0:08:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clause! Well, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.35,0:08:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw Hiroyuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.56,0:08:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I saw him when I was visiting\Na certain noble's mansion today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.90,0:08:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he doing at a noble's mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.11,0:08:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.86,0:08:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.16,0:08:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, Hiroyuki!\NWait, Genzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.91,0:09:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.45,0:09:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring you back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.33,0:09:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.51,0:09:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here, Catherine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.77,0:09:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria, why don't you\Ngive Catherine a treat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.77,0:09:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Catherine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.49,0:09:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.28,0:09:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I give her back?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.70,0:09:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I paid a high price to buy her\Nfrom a merchant this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.45,0:09:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Catherine's taken\Na liking to my Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.50,0:09:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name's Hiroyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.09,0:09:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody stole him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.63,0:09:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not my problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.17,0:09:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's now Catherine.\NMy animal. That I bought.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.93,0:10:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Hiroyuki was originally ours,\Nand we'd like him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.89,0:10:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shigure, what he's saying isn't wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.65,0:10:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.86,0:10:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Hiroyuki was stolen, if he bought him\Nwithout knowing that, he did nothing wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what's going on,\Nbut that's brilliant, Mistress!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You keep your mouth shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.29,0:10:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then there's no problem\Nif we buy him back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Princess Buttocks...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.75,0:10:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.17,0:10:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much did you pay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.17,0:10:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the receipt from\Nwhen I purchased him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.05,0:10:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so expensive...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.14,0:10:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father, Catherine just...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.44,0:10:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.87,0:11:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it yummy, Catherine?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.83,0:11:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father, she says it's yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.17,0:11:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had my chefs make it\Nfor her especially.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.63,0:11:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroyuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.88,0:11:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the perfect chance\Nto get Genzo in my debt!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.89,0:11:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There should be enough money\Nin the castle treasury...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.77,0:11:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I buy back that little animal,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.23,0:11:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Genzo will have to do what I tell him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.44,0:11:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can get him to\Ndo his duty as hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.11,0:11:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're leaving, Shigure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.78,0:11:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure, Genzo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.70,0:11:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.53,0:11:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.50,0:11:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you understand. Now go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.59,0:11:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Genzo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.96,0:12:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Genzo...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.38,0:12:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you... crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.10,0:12:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a wuss!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.77,0:12:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be happy, Hiroyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.19,0:12:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, was Catherine your dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.12,0:12:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.49,0:12:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been with me through\Nso much sorrow and joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.00,0:12:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a part of my family!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.34,0:12:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.55,0:12:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Maria?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.55,0:12:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I give Catherine back to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.59,0:12:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, Maria?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.35,0:12:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, I paid for her...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.73,0:12:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'd had Catherine\Never since I was little,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.48,0:13:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then she went to another\Nperson's house, I'd be sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.19,0:13:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I think she's very sad now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.74,0:13:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.78,0:13:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.66,0:13:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if that's how it's going to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.66,0:13:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't let you have her for free!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.13,0:13:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I paid all this money!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.80,0:13:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need at least half...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.34,0:13:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Half? Even that's too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.47,0:13:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.30,0:13:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're ten years too young to look\Nat a man with eyes like that, Maria...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.94,0:13:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, half of the half, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.53,0:13:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, half of that!\NActually, half of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.99,0:13:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And another half... and another half...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.29,0:13:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet another half...\Nand another half...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.59,0:14:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more half!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to pay that much!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.01,0:14:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't have that much money,\NCatherine is better off at our home!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.51,0:14:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.06,0:14:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we still don't have that kind of money!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.44,0:14:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mistress, look at what\NGenzo did to my stomach!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.82,0:14:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please rub this painkiller lotion on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.07,0:14:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let your pretty fingers\Nrun across my belly...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.91,0:14:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.96,0:14:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without money, Hiroyuki will...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.04,0:14:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria was a nice child, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.21,0:14:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Genzo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.84,0:14:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroyuki may be happy with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.64,0:14:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can have his fill of yummy food...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.31,0:14:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's gotten into you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:15:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I really wanted\Nto do with my pet shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.81,0:15:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meeting an animal.\NInteracting with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.61,0:15:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sharing in their joys...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.19,0:15:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So maybe I'm better\Noff letting him go...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.53,0:15:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really sure, Genzo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.75,0:15:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.80,0:15:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this money?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.30,0:15:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know we had\Nso much in this house...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.39,0:15:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was saving it in case\Nwe ever needed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.48,0:15:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew if I told you about it,\Nyou'd just spend it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.48,0:15:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can use it to buy back Hiroyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.86,0:15:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shigure...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.49,0:15:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.86,0:15:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping we could use it\Nto open the pet shop, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.82,0:16:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether we use it now or use it in\Nthe future, it's still there to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.08,0:16:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a deal, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye, Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.63,0:16:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name's Hiroyuki.\NCome by and play sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.43,0:16:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, can I ask something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.43,0:16:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was the merchant\Nwho sold you Hiroyuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were three of them actually,\Nand they were quite strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.65,0:16:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bearded man with an eye patch.\NA wolf beastman and a cat beast woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.20,0:16:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think it would go this well!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.74,0:16:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard he was running around\Nthe whole town crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.71,0:16:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I being petted?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.25,0:16:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It just feels right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.96,0:16:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't had such\Ngood drink in a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.17,0:16:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drink, drink! This is\Nthe drink of victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.84,0:16:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gulp it all down...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.89,0:17:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you thought you could\Nsell Hiroyuki, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.73,0:17:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not even worth petting anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.28,0:17:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just spent all the money to open\Nthis shop you're smashing up, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.49,0:17:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.12,0:17:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear my bones snapping!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.59,0:17:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.51,0:17:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.97,0:17:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Genzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.98,0:17:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've avenged you, Hiroyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.60,0:17:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not dead, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.11,0:17:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back, Genzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.45,0:17:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now use this money to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.41,0:18:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.41,0:18:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Hiroyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.16,0:18:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous out there,\Nso sleep in my bed tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.25,0:18:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.55,0:18:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Birdy! Mr. Woof!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.26,0:18:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are these demon beasts doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.35,0:18:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Genzo, did you bring home even more...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.02,0:18:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This smell...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.81,0:18:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody's inside our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.11,0:18:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.28,0:18:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lindabulea, I never thought\Nwe'd meet again like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.11,0:18:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.70,0:18:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget again...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.45,0:18:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Draculius\NJoanna Joannascore...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We meet again, Genzo Shibata.\NMy name is Draculius Joanna Joannascore...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.54,0:18:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Animal Mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.59,0:18:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one who attacked\Nthe orc village?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.17,0:18:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.84,0:19:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, MAO.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.89,0:19:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.06,0:19:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you really do know\Nthe Demon King from another world?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.52,0:19:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.23,0:19:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was you who summoned the\NDemon King from another world?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.61,0:19:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what about you? You should be\Ndefeating the hero, not living with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.74,0:19:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a traitor to our lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.37,0:19:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.74,0:19:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I've got my reasons, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.04,0:19:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you lost to the hero and begged\Nhim to save your life, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.42,0:19:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cowardly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.13,0:19:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you don't get to talk\Nabout her like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.47,0:19:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, lesser vampire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.26,0:19:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Know your place!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.97,0:19:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.43,0:19:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a match!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.10,0:19:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.02,0:19:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.77,0:19:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Joanna, what's a "match"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.44,0:20:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you. A "match" is a... a battle\Nto the death they do in other worlds!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.82,0:20:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two men enter, one man ends up dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.41,0:20:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.53,0:20:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lindabulea, I challenge\Nyou to a "match," too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.04,0:20:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Joanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.33,0:20:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I don't know who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.13,0:20:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're bothering\Nthe neighbors, so quiet down...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.30,0:20:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.42,0:20:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Clause! Where did you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.76,0:20:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking it's about time\Nfor a second tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.93,0:20:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're doing that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.43,0:20:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fighting tournament? Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.81,0:20:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bury you in front of a huge crowd!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.90,0:20:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, don't run when\Nyou fight me, Animal Mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.24,0:20:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I'll pay you back\Nfor what you did!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.53,0:20:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight me, Lindabulea!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.45,0:20:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mistress, we can't lose this fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.95,0:20:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another tournament?\NWill there be more yummy food?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.29,0:21:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it! This is our\Nchance to be rich, Genzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.76,0:21:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pay you back, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.93,0:21:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.22,0:21:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a fight, MAO!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.86,0:21:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MAO... I'm up against\Na real pro wrestler!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.78,0:21:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A totally different fight than\Nthe amateurs I've battled thus far.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.79,0:21:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Carmilla? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.55,0:21:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone I need to beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.30,0:21:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm willing to do whatever it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.55,0:21:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Genzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.80,0:21:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please... please teach me pro wrestling!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.48,0:22:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.12,0:23:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: "Pride x Loyalty."